1 (1) THE value of the entire parcel determined under § 14–707 of this
2 subtitle [multiplied by the] MINUS THE TOTAL AMOUNT OF EACH OUTSTANDING LIEN
3 ON THE PROPERTY, INCLUDING ANY MORTGAGE, DEED OF TRUST, TAX LIEN, AND
4 JUDGMENT LIEN; AND
5 (2) THE cotenant’s fractional ownership of the entire parcel.
6 SECTION 2. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall be construed to
7 apply only prospectively and may not be applied or interpreted to have any effect on or
8 application to any partition action filed before the effective date of this Act.
9 SECTION 3. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall take effect
10 October 1, 2025.

